  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1527960/extras/f13efa68c739086211e6c0cd80e1cf7b.avif?t=1770598485\" width=626 height=124 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>RULES</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Fix problems in time;</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Random Problems by Levels;</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Configuration issues are simple;</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Swap problems are complex;</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> One computer at a time;</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> User chases you and drains your energy;</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> No power? One less life;</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> No time? One less life;</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> No lives? Go back to the beginning of the game;</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 5 pink disks equal life;</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 1 green disk equal to 15 seconds;</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Did you spend a lot? Wait to load everything;</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>CONTROL</strong></h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Use arrow keys to move;</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Use \"SHIFT\" to run;</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Use \"C\" to move the camera;</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Use \"ENTER\" or \"SPACE\" for any action;</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>GAMEPLAY</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Enemies chase at different speeds;</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> The game has 20 levels;</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Difficulty is defined by luck;</li></ul>",
